
Endeavour OS Legacy install
Used on Lenovo Thinkcentre M81
Flash drive I create on Windows 8.1 with rufus formatted as MBR
(on Linux with dd command do not boot)

Grub loader, because there is no boot loader

12 mb unformated
17 gb swap swap
42 gb root
50 gb home


--------------------------------------------
This is UEFI installation it not work on M81
Flash drive can be created on linux with dd command

Endeavour OS UEFI
512MB fat32 /boot/efi - bios-grub, boot
35-42GB ext4 / - root
50GB ext4 /home

